Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來請作自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出灰  篝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出灰同學  除了名字以外再說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  篝她有些不善言辭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你看她像不像佐佐木望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像  真的好像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是毒舌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  篝  這頭髮是染出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是煩死了  銀蒼蠅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說銀蒼蠅～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一來就和同學們打成一片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很意外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要上學也是她主動提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是峰迴路轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信  她究竟是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是黃泉的心情感染了她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡學姐來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  黃泉抱歉  我離開一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺總是看到  她們兩人如此形影不離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕微扭傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時不聲不響就倒下了  真嚇了我們一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嚇了一跳  原來真有人因為扭傷而昏過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說得好像事不關己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  真的太好了  小幡學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  真的太好了我  哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  預賽大概是不能上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預賽晉級就看這傢伙好好表現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  小幡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不在  我們社團每天就像守靈一樣死氣沉沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  那午休時趕快去訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳踝有點疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烹飪社？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就你一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只一個人  對吧  篝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去參觀一下  前輩也說想跟你聊聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點悵然若失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從小就在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總以為她不能離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了絕對不讓她感到孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不從她身邊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝吧  咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使小鳥遊不在  也不會有人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有人那麼需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人…需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  往積極的方面想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意思是小鳥遊沒必要感到自責
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  優
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間沒法一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優也跟你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起是說？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  畢竟是同一個社團  為什麼這麼問
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  那裡  把巴迪克大街賣給篝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  賣吧賣吧賣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行就是不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小篝只有在這種時候才這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦交上了朋友  對我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴迪克大街就賣給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不在昨晚準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚累壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以咬著麵包出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  太沒教養了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想試試了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也試試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.39,0:08:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小篝  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  黃泉去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去上學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉好遲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接你的時候你已經出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說一聲就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算啥  你在生氣什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉…小篝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得要給什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣賓夕法尼亞大街就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賓夕法尼亞大街？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前覺得自己要是沒有了黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會一事無成  什麼都幹不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在  學習也跟得上  又受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都盡善盡美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人指出才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去總是依賴著黃泉幫我做事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要替黃泉做點什麼才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不懂如何為他人付出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  怎麼樣我才能為黃泉做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  畫風好像變得很灰暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來能成為一幅不錯的畫的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那態度也太差了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我不在  也不會有人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人會需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我不在  世界也不會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天小篝已經回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是小鳥遊你把她帶回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早上還不是對她指指點點的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺著一副家長的臭架子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  想一個人獨佔小篝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親自下廚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得加入了烹飪社了  今天也應該做了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪德琳蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  就是這一類的  她絕對會開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉會開心…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來我不得不照顧篝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…突然說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  篝和別人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也完全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不在意！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說那樣我更開心！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意啊  篝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  篝來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  出來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易她願意去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想見！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請轉交這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又沒和黃泉一起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然去接過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（謝謝你擔心我  不過不用來看望了）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得黃泉最近沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又什麼都不肯告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊的地址
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和她交朋友  和小鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優  真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…怎麼了啊  真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊  聲音再大點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾一下可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被大家嘲笑  真的很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以傷害了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  我還有社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不能原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會和大家解釋的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不太明白你所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不能原諒  生氣什麼的都沒有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你我都不怎麼認識…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝今天也來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然發了那樣的郵件…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透…真透的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我是優）
