Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（朋友）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（真透也很擔心哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透的…朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼啊  算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼啊  算什麼啊  算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼啊  算什麼啊  算什麼啊  算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝她還等著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝她還需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…只有篝還…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.98,0:17:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.27,0:17:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  淋濕了  淋濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塑膠傘也壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶咖  奶咖…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱熱的奶咖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是點心？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這次是巧克力餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝呢  一直覺得該為黃泉做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都讓你照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得好好報答一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.12,0:17:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不報答的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉就不會放開篝的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉呀…雖然說篝和別人交朋友感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那大概是在逞強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛奶  加熱開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是讓你逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很對不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝呀  覺得以前自己沒有黃泉就什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得…但是  篝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對我來說  沒有黃泉就一無所能這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經記不太清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉為篝做了好多
